{"id": 2027, "genre": 1000, "title": "那些“专为亚洲人打造”的产品，你为啥不太买账？", "description": "专为亚洲人发明的7日瘦腿操，该胖还是胖。(题图来自：GIPHY)", "record_count": 6582, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171122183109P59DirX0c7BIA31e.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-23T00:17:54Z", "questions": [{"id": 3325, "title": "那些“专为亚洲人打造”的产品，你为啥不太买账？", "content": "那些专为亚洲人打造的产品，你为啥并不care？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 250359, "content": "早有了解决方案，不用买什么专为亚洲人设计的墨镜，买那种带鼻托的就行", "image": "img/option/option/20171122183201BVGspKiz8LOvhc19.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250362, "content": "成分、设计没差别，但“专为亚洲人设计”就更贵了的护肤品、床垫之类的", "image": "img/option/option/20171122184923lNKjMOoFXEdR8c7Q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250363, "content": "越帮越忙，西方品牌服装买惯了s/m/l，换成日本码1/2/3尺寸缩水，拿不准穿什么码", "image": "img/option/option/20171122185459K0xmsOzUydnjXlYh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250365, "content": "强化刻板印象，为亚洲人出的粉底色号都和迪士尼花木兰肤色匹配", "image": "img/option/option/20171122183508luRb2NeFJhgXIfas.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250368, "content": "归类笼统，我会根据发质来选择洗发水，而非买一款不明所以的“专为亚洲人设计”", "image": "img/option/option/20171122184351dlfNkJiyBLT4DXu0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250369, "content": "没有针对性，亚洲人牙龈脆弱…请试试这款功能一模一样的电动牙刷", "image": "img/option/option/20171122184415UNbLolHRQZvaDAw1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250370, "content": "找错重点，不是“粉质细”就适合亚洲人，粉质和显色程度跟喜欢的妆感有关", "image": "img/option/option/20171122184725IFPGKQgaMYn1D0oz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250490, "content": "不明所以，专为亚洲人设计的香水、健身操，不知道独特的点是什么", "image": "img/option/option/20171123084645QkGy6qZz3umcYf9p.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}